olume. They come with tubes installed, but are ready to be set up tubeless.</p><p><a href=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/05095143/fezzari-lone-peak-kids-mountain-bike-5.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/05095143/fezzari-lone-peak-kids-mountain-bike-5.jpg\" alt=\"fezzari lone peak kids mountain bike shown from front\" width=\"1400\" height=\"933\" data-ezsrcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/05095143/fezzari-lone-peak-kids-mountain-bike-5.jpg 1400w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/05095143/fezzari-lone-peak-kids-mountain-bike-5-297x198.jpg 297w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/05095143/fezzari-lone-peak-kids-mountain-bike-5-800x533.jpg 800w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/05095143/fezzari-lone-peak-kids-mountain-bike-5-120x80.jpg 120w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/05095143/fezzari-lone-peak-kids-mountain-bike-5-768x512.jpg 768w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/05095143/fezzari-lone-peak-kids-mountain-bike-5-696x464.jpg 696w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/05095143/fezzari-lone-peak-kids-mountain-bike-5-1068x712.jpg 1068w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/05095143/fezzari-lone-peak-kids-mountain-bike-5-630x420.jpg 630w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1400px) 100vw, 1400px\" ezimgfmt=\"rs rscb28 src ng ngcb28 srcset\" data-ezsrc=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/05095143/fezzari-lone-peak-kids-mountain-bike-5.jpg\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/05095143/fezzari-lone-peak-kids-mountain-bike-5.jpg 1400w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/05095143/fezzari-lone-peak-kids-mountain-bike-5-297x198.jpg 297w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/05095143/fezzari-lone-peak-kids-mountain-bike-5-800x533.jpg 800w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/05095143/fezzari-lone-peak-kids-mountain-bike-5-120x80.jpg 120w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/05095143/fezzari-lone-peak-kids-mountain-bike-5-768x512.jpg 768w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/05095143/fezzari-lone-peak-kids-mountain-bike-5-696x464.jpg 696w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/05095143/fezzari-lone-peak-kids-mountain-bike-5-1068x712.jpg 1068w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/05095143/fezzari-lone-peak-kids-mountain-bike-5-630x420.jpg 630w\"></a></p><p>The headtube is tapered, and they say you can upgrade to a 100mm travel fork, but the stock fork is a straight 1-1/8″ steerer SR Suntour XCR Air fork with 80mm of travel. It has a lighter spring setup to help it move through the travel even under smaller, lighter riders.</p><p>A 67º head angle gives it a modern take on aggressive geometry, just with a kid’s sizing in mind.</p><p><a href=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/05095138/fezzari-lone-peak-kids-mountain-bike-4.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/05095138/fezzari-lone-peak-kids-mountain-bike-4.jpg\" alt